data.description: WOW! This beautifully updated Alligator Point home is a MUST SEE! It features an open floor plan complete with vinyl flooring in the living room and porcelain tile throughout the kitchen and bedrooms. Both bathrooms have been updated with new vanities and marble floor showers. Other features include new metal roof with gutters installed in 2021, fish cleaning area, outdoor shower, screened-in downstairs and covered parking for trucks and boats.   The boat ramp is right around the corner, giving you access to the bay and gulf in minutes, or choose to store your boat at Alligator Point marina. Explore the white sandy beaches of Alligator Point, Bald Point and Mashes Sands from this perfect location, or grab your bike and connect to the Alligator Point/Coastal Trail bike path.   As an added advantage, the seller is giving $3,000 towards closing cost assistance or concessions. Bring your offer!
